bind.jr:constraintMsg:
The worker ID must be a number between 0 and 999, 3 digts, and can't start with a zero.
ID ya mfanyakazi lazima iwe kati ya 0 na 999, tarakamu 3, na haiwezi kuanza na sifuri.
